description:
The data mimemap is a named character vector that stores the filename
extensions and the corresponding MIME types, e.g. c(html = 'text/html',
pdf = 'application/pdf', ...). The character vector mimeextra stores
some additional types that we know, such as Markdown files (<U+2018>.md<U+2019>), or R
scripts (<U+2018>.R<U+2019>).
